Phoneme

Class Phoneme

  • java.lang.Object
    • Phoneme.Phoneme

  • public class Phoneme
extends java.lang.Object
    Phoneme class used to calculate the confusion costs contains getters and setters for the different categories derived from IPA table. Self explaining. See package Phoneme.Categories for the different category values.
    Author:
    7twiefel
